USAGE

    <random (o) interval="$INTERVAL">
        < ... commands>
    </random>

    $INTERVAL           - The delay in ms between next time it is executed. By default it is 0 ms.

    This block can be nested:

    <random>
        <random>
            commands...
        </random>
        <random>
            commands...
        </random>
    </random>